				</entry> 
				<entry colname="col2"> 
				  <p>An aggregation of cards that you create or that have been
					 shared with you by other users or from Adobe 
					 <keyword>Marketing Cloud</keyword> solutions. 
				  </p> aggregation of boards. In the feed you hid things. In the
				  board you delete things. Hide vs delete 
