				  scope="local">Boards</xref> 
				</entry> 
				<entry colname="col2"> 
				  <p>A collection of cards (reports, images, and documents, for
					 example) related to a particular project or a campaign. You can use boards to
					 collect and curate cards that contain supporting facts for an insight or an
					 idea. You can keep your boards private or you can share them with other users
					 to create a collaborative space for your team. 
				  </p> 
